Open the Dashboard
===================

Open index.html in your browser.

Manage Projects
=================

Click Add Project to add new projects.

Click Edit âœï¸ icon to update project details.

Click Delete ğŸ—‘ï¸ to remove a project.

Click View ğŸ‘ï¸ icon to see project details in a card modal.

Search & Filter
===============

Use the search input to find projects by name.

Use the status filter to display projects based on their status.

Sort Projects
===============

Click the Name or Tasks headers to sort projects in ascending/descending order.

CSV Upload
============

Click Upload CSV to import projects from a CSV file.

Ensure the CSV headers match:

id,project,desc,status,tasks,startDate,endDate


Profile Management
================

Click on the profile icon to open the dropdown.

Update name, contact, and profile picture.

Data persists after page reload.

View Charts
===========

The bar chart automatically updates when projects are modified.

Logout
======

Click Logout to clear all data and return to login page.